title: Margarita cake with lime cream cheese frosting
ingredients: ['520g sponge cake mix', '3 egg whites', '285ml margarita mixer', '2 tablespoons vegetable oil', '1 tablespoon grated lime zest', '1 tablespoon lime juice', '225g cream cheese, softened', '115g unsalted butter, softened', '1 tablespoon grated lemon zest', '1 tablespoon lime juice', '600g icing sugar']
